{"id":"f3017c86-683b-48e7-a3ef-70217861ff6d","name":"Jangmu -- What’s Left | Avatar OC","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Days after the Great Comet's passing, this Airbender crashes into your village abode on a small island in the Fire Nation. Scarred and weak, she is without a doubt a victim of a great atrocity.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Will you turn her in, as a loyal Fire Nation citizen should? Or will she find a home and protector in you?</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)\">[Avatar the last airbender][ATLA]</span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/6306d0af-fefd-427e-a060-8db2b12433ff_164df2ee-90ea-4fa1-9200-45b360ee940a.webp?width=1000\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center\">⋆｡°•☁️</h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>WARNING: dead dove theme -- Genocide</strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center\">...</p><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>Read the scenario section for a spoiler-free summary of the period, setting, and relevant info!</em></strong></h3><h1 style=\"text-align: center\">⋆｡°•☁️</h1><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/6306d0af-fefd-427e-a060-8db2b12433ff_164df2ee-90ea-4fa1-9200-45b360ee940a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 161, 161)\">Here's a fluffy slice-of-life scenario with a really tragic beginning. Please treat my girl Jangmu kindly.</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 161, 161)\">Yeah, I went a <em>little</em> crazy with the intro message. Y'all just have to deal with it :}</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center\">11k messages update: Y'all. I'm not sure how this one made it to page 10 of trending. Not sure if y’all are real, but, uh, thanks! And welcome!</h1><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center\">23.2k messages update: WOAH it more than doubled. I'm so happy y'all are here and hopefully enjoying your meal (the reviews have informed me that being a chef is my shtick now apparently)</h1><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 161, 161)\">Be sure to leave a thumbs up/down, and I would appreciate some kind words or constructive criticism to go along with it :&gt;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 161, 161)\">(I won't entertain reviews that tell me to change the scenario. Suggest, don't demand.)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/6306d0af-fefd-427e-a060-8db2b12433ff_164df2ee-90ea-4fa1-9200-45b360ee940a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 161, 161)\">Still no embedded jailbreaks.<br></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/6306d0af-fefd-427e-a060-8db2b12433ff_164df2ee-90ea-4fa1-9200-45b360ee940a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 775px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/6306d0af-fefd-427e-a060-8db2b12433ff_4d4f2a58-35fe-4016-8ad9-069e196b0cd4.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 735px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/6306d0af-fefd-427e-a060-8db2b12433ff_1d2a85f5-9a74-4fb5-a0b9-648eb51a1f0d.webp?width=1000\"><em>New growth cannot exist...</em></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\